rComments: One of my favorite profs in UTM. experienced lecturer with a caring heart for his students and a passion for writing. Just wanted to say Thank you Professor Penhale =)

One of the best profs I've ever had.  His class improved my writing 100%, and gave me so much confidence in my writing.  Even if you say something completely wrong, he'll just nod and go, "Okay!  That's good!"  Absolutely nothing negative about the guy.

David is not only a wonderful prof, but a wonderful person. His lectures are structured, but he is just so sweet. Honestly, you will just want to pinch his cheeks, he's so cute. He's also very helpful. TAKE HIS CLASS, YOU WILL NOT BE DISAPPOINTED!!!
